<p><strong>Time required:</strong> 30-60 minutes per page
<strong>Difficulty:</strong> Beginner to Intermediate
<strong>What you need:</strong> Access to your site's HTML or CMS, Google Search Console</p>
<h2>Rich Snippets vs Featured Snippets vs SERP Features</h2>
<p>Before implementing anything, understand the terminology. These three terms describe different things.</p>
